query:
SELECT 
  at.id as auditTypeId,
  at.auditName,
  atem.id as templateId,
  atem.templateName,
  COUNT(DISTINCT ats.id) as sectionCount,
  COUNT(atq.id) as questionCount
FROM auditTypes at
LEFT JOIN auditTemplates atem ON at.id = atem.auditTypeId AND atem.isActive = 1
LEFT JOIN auditTemplateSections ats ON atem.id = ats.auditTemplateId
LEFT JOIN auditTemplateQuestions atq ON ats.id = atq.auditTemplateSectionId
WHERE at.auditName LIKE '%daily%'
GROUP BY at.id, at.auditName, atem.id, atem.templateName;
